GTAV Classic% Speedrun of GDQ Submission (See Description!) (6:14:31)
description:
GDQ (Games Done Quick) is a big speedrun convention that raises money for charity with 24/7 speedruns for two weeks. In the runs, the runners explain the entire run in detail to explain what they are doing in the run to save time, along with giving general info about whats happening in the game, so I don't read chat and basically make a live Casual VS Speedrun episode.

This version of the the video has music and donation alerts, there will be a version on youtube with no music/alerts uploaded if you prefer that style.

To GDQ People: if there is a problem with language or graphics of the game, we have mods than can fix it the community will allow me to use during a special GDQ run. The game is quite moddable and anything offending can be removed, even up to leaving all dialogue but just muting the voicelines, would just need a few weeks to prepare :)

GTAV Speedrun Guide: Father/Son (See Description)
description:
This is a GDQ style explanation of the cycles of getting Franklin up and down from the boat during father son. keyword, cycles. 

As well, you want to shoot the first guy slightly later than i do here, as it'll skip a bit more animations from franklin before he recovers and jimmy comes out. Also when I say "pick jimmy up in 4 seconds" i meant "within 4 seconds", earlier is fine.
